1.title: Daron wyatt
1.plot: When a young woman is mysteriously murdered, Det. Daron Wyatt must use behavioral science, overlooked evidence and a chilling interrogation tape to solve the case and bring closure to her family, and himself.

2.title: Jerry clark
2.plot: The infamous Erie, PA bombing case is widely known for its disturbing and bewildering twists and turns. But for lead FBI investigator the pursuit of solving the puzzle takes a heavy toll on his life.

3.title: John garcia
3.plot: John Garcia investigates the murder of Oscar-winning Cambodian actor and activist Haing Ngor.

4.title: Dimitry ruvin
4.plot: John Garcia investigates the murder of Oscar-winning Cambodian actor and activist Haing Ngor.

5.title: Terry king
5.plot: Detective Terry King of Camden, NJ gets called to the scene of a homicide that changes his life forever. The investigation of a brutal death causes him to form a lasting bond with a surviving victim who holds the key to finding justice.

6.title: Lane youmans
6.plot: Det. Lane Youmans becomes convinced about a connection between two brutal murders that happened on the same logging road years apart.

7.title: Joe costolnick
7.plot: Rookie Detective Joe Costolnick uses a sense of empathy to find the killer of an unnamed woman in rural Georgia.

8.title: Danny agan
8.plot: Survivors of a serial rapist who terrorized Atlanta help Det. Danny Agan pursue the attacker in a two-decade-long investigation that ends with the help of Agan's very own son joining the force and taking over the case.

imdb.title: The Price of Duty
plot: "_The Price of Duty_ (qv)" follows dedicated detectives from across the country as they recount their stories of complex cases that have emotionally impacted and changed their lives forever.
